"                </div>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    ${partner.salutation},\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    We very warmly thank you for choosing to sponsor ${firstname} and to be on our side to free one more child from extreme poverty.\n"
"<br/>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"Despite our previous reminder, <!-- Keep space -->\n"
"% if lsv_dd and not lsv_form_received:\n"
"    the banking authorization form is still missing. Therefore, your sponsorship is not activated. <b>We kindly ask you to send the filled form within 15 days</b>. Otherwise we will be forced to end your sponsorship and look for another sponsor for "
"${firstname}. Thanks for making the support of this child a priority.\n"
"    <br/>\n"
"    <br/>\n"
"    If you would like to use a monthly permanent order instead, please contact us.\n"
"% else:\n"
"    we notice that your first payment is still missing. Your sponsorship is thus not activated. <b>We kindly ask you to transfer the amount of CHF ${'%d' | format(amount)}.- within ${extension} days using the payment slip attached</b>. Otherwise we will be "
"forced to end your sponsorship and look for another sponsor for ${firstname}.\n"
"    <br/>\n"
"    <br/>\n"
"    If this letter crosses with your payment, please accept our thanks and ignore this notice. Thanks for making the payment of your sponsorship a priority.\n"
"% endif\n"
"<br/>\n"
"<br/> \n"
"We wish you plenty of blessings through this sponsorship which gives ${firstname} the opportunity of a better future.\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    Yours sincerely\n"
"                </p>\n"
"            "
