"<div>\n"
"                    % set sponsorships = object.get_objects()\n"
"                    % set child = sponsorships.mapped('child_id')\n"
"                    % set one = len(child) == 1\n"
"                    % set name = child.get_list('preferred_name', 3, 'your children')\n"
"                    % if one:\n"
"                        % set lifecycle = child.mapped('lifecycle_ids') and child.mapped('lifecycle_ids')[0]\n"
"                    % endif\n"
"                    % set sub = sponsorships.mapped('sub_sponsorship_id.child_id')\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    ${object.partner_id.salutation},\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    We would like to sincerely thank you for investing in the life of ${name}.\n"
"                    As you know, a sponsorship with Compassion usually ends when the child has graduated. However, as you have experienced, sometimes a child leaves the sponsorship program earlier than expected.\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    % if one:\n"
"                        Our partner office in ${child.project_id.country_id.name} has now informed us that ${child.get('your sponsored child')}, ${name} has ended the sponsorship because ${lifecycle.translate('request_reason')}.\n"
"                        <br/>\n"
"                    % else:\n"
"                        We received the news that ${child.get('your sponsored child')} have ended the sponsorship, with the following reasons:\n"
"                        <ul>\n"
"                            % for one_child in child:\n"
"                                % set lifecycle = one_child.mapped('lifecycle_ids') and one_child.mapped('lifecycle_ids')[0]\n"
"                                <li>${one_child.preferred_name} : ${lifecycle.translate('request_reason')}.</li>\n"
"                            % endfor\n"
"                        </ul>\n"
"                    % endif\n"
"                    We are very sorry and apologize that your sponsorship for ${name} was terminated due to unforeseen circumstances.  However, we are certain that your support was not in vain, and will leave a blessing in ${child.get('his')} life!\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    % if one:\n"
"                        The local staff have informed us that ${name} is healthy. ${child.get('his').title()} current goals are: ${lifecycle.get_list('future_hope_ids.value')}.\n"
"                    % endif\n"
"                    We sincerely thank you for your commitment to ${child.get('this child')}.  Thanks to your regular support, ${name} ${child.get('was')} able to attend school, receive clothing, medical treatment, and balanced, nutritious meals. ${child."
"get('he').title()} ${child.get('was')} also able to participate in activities that have helped ${child.get('him')}) develop both socially and spiritually. We hope that these seeds will bear fruit in ${child.get('his')} ${'life' if one else 'lives'}.  The "
"family has also benefited from the support of your sponsorship.  They have been encouraged and have been able to participate in various activities and trainings organized by the Center.  Please continue to bless ${name} with prayers of protection and "
"guidance.\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    % if sub:\n"
"                        % if one:\n"
"                            As you already know, the plight of children living in poverty is enormous.  For instance, ${sub.preferred_name} ${sub.project_id.country_id.preposition} ${sub.project_id.country_id.name} is one of them.  Would you consider and be "
"ready to sponsor ${sub.get('him')}?  We would like to send you information about ${sub.preferred_name} within 15 days to begin a new sponsorship. However, if you would like to support a child from another country, have questions, concerns, or would no longer "
"like to be a sponsor, please do not hesitate to contact us. We can be reached by phone at 031 552 21 25 or by e-mail at: parrainage@compassion.ch\n"
"                        % else:\n"
"                            As you already know, the plight of children living in poverty is enormous.  For instance, ${sub[0].preferred_name} ${sub[0].project_id.country_id.preposition} ${sub[0].project_id.country_id.name} is one of them.  Would you consider "
